body:
Since this gem of a cover dropped through [**Triple J**](http://www.abc.net.au/triplej/media/s3427607.htm) radio over the weekend, I haven’t been able to drag my ears away from it. On paper it’s utterly perfect, with [Chairlift’s](http://admin.crackintheroad.com/music/14253-stream-chairlift-something/ "Stream: Chairlift – Something") Caroline guesting on [**Das Racist**’s](http://admin.crackintheroad.com/music/4328-new-das-racist-swate-feat-lakutis/ "New: Das Racist- ‘Swate’ Feat. Lakutis") brilliant [“**_Fashion Party_**”](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t0sqqi0G5a8&feature=related) 2 years ago. In reality it managed to be even better. Caroline’s voice more than manages to live up to **Beyonce**’s original rendition and **Kool A.D**’s deadpan flows of consciousnesses poke fun at everything from the **Common/Drake** beef to, well I honestly I have no idea; but it feels like he’s making fun of something.

Stream the live performance below.

